Description
The Note Taker is an application that allows users to write, save, and retrieve notes seamlessly. This application offers an interactive and user-friendly interface, making it easy to jot down thoughts, tasks, or any kind of notes.

Features
Landing Page: On accessing the application, users are greeted with a landing page containing a link to the notes section.

Notes Page: The notes page showcases:

A list of saved notes on the left.
A section to write a new note on the right.
A save icon to store the notes.
A write icon to clear fields for a new note.
Interactive UI:

Upon writing a note, a save icon becomes visible.
Saved notes can be viewed or edited by clicking on them.
The write icon refreshes the note-taking section.
Technologies Used
Express.js: Powers the back-end, providing a robust set of features to facilitate routing and API interactions.

JSON: Utilized for storing and retrieving the user notes, ensuring data persistence.

Setup and Usage
Prerequisites
Node.js
